1423
01:12:36,395 --> 01:12:38,397
[laughs]

1424
01:12:38,441 --> 01:12:41,400
I got the first email
last night...

1425
01:12:41,444 --> 01:12:45,056
right before I drifted off
to sleep.

1426
01:12:45,099 --> 01:12:47,406
I was pretty excited.

1427
01:12:47,450 --> 01:12:50,409
And then this morning,
I wake up,

1428
01:12:50,453 --> 01:12:51,976
and what do you know?

1429
01:12:52,019 --> 01:12:56,415
We're accepted
to another film festival!

1430
01:12:56,459 --> 01:12:57,590
Two!

1431
01:12:57,634 --> 01:12:59,070
Hi!

1432
01:12:59,113 --> 01:13:00,158
- Hi.

1433
01:13:00,201 --> 01:13:03,379
