01:13:09,994 --> 01:13:12,649
Now the fun part begins.

1439
01:13:12,692 --> 01:13:15,565
Now it's gonna be the juice.

1440
01:13:15,608 --> 01:13:17,305
[laughs]

1441
01:13:26,053 --> 01:13:27,664
- We'll take...

1442
01:13:32,799 --> 01:13:36,760
The plan for today is,
