1455
01:14:06,529 --> 01:14:08,487
Right now, Kit Farrell
from "Pandora's Hope"

1456
01:14:08,531 --> 01:14:10,010
joins us right now.

1457
01:14:10,054 --> 01:14:11,708
Tell us about
this wonderful movie.

1458
01:14:11,751 --> 01:14:14,972
- Oh, I'm so excited
about this--my debut project.

1459
01:14:17,191 --> 01:14:20,804
Hawaii's island of Kauai
is many things to many people.

1460
01:14:20,847 --> 01:14:23,415
- Things that you normally
only read about

1461
01:14:23,459 --> 01:14:26,374
in "Discover Magazine"
or something.

1462
01:14:26,418 --> 01:14:29,465
It's not often you see
shark's teeth in a human.

1463
01:14:29,508 --> 01:14:33,120
But, you know, they're
functioning perfectly.

1464
01:14:48,048 --> 01:14:50,007
- I was wondering,
do we push this?

1465
01:14:50,050 --> 01:14:52,705
Do I go up there
and serve wine?

1466
01:14:52,749 --> 01:14:54,315
[laughter]

1467
01:14:54,359 --> 01:14:56,622
- With the teeth?
- With the teeth.

1468
01:15:00,365 --> 01:15:02,498
- To me, it's another level
of absurdity

1469
01:15:02,541 --> 01:15:06,850
that I can't stop myself
from wanting to do.

1470
01:15:13,900 --> 01:15:15,946
- People might find it odd

1471
01:15:15,989 --> 01:15:20,167
that you're using the stem
cells of a different species

1472
