1475
01:15:31,570 --> 01:15:35,095
It was as if Joe
was born with those teeth.

1476
01:15:35,139 --> 01:15:37,881
[applause]

1477
01:15:37,924 --> 01:15:39,709
- I'm Kit Farrell.

1478
01:15:39,752 --> 01:15:42,233
- That group was basically
to make it more transparent,

1479
01:15:42,276 --> 01:15:43,930
as they say.

