1485
01:15:57,117 --> 01:15:59,163
It has to do with stem cells.

1486
01:16:19,487 --> 01:16:23,970
- My stories may take off
and be an instant--

1487
01:16:24,014 --> 01:16:26,233
everyone has to read it.

1488
01:16:26,277 --> 01:16:30,673
Or they may be a slow,
in the back burner, you know,

1489
01:16:30,716 --> 01:16:34,372
takes time for this
to come around.

1490
01:16:34,415 --> 01:16:38,289
And I have to have
the openness,

1491
01:16:38,332 --> 01:16:41,901
the flexibility
to let that happen.

1492
01:16:45,165 --> 01:16:50,518
I have planted seeds
of thought.

1493
01:16:50,562 --> 01:16:55,088
And seeds of thought
hopefully will grow.

1494
01:17:01,834 --> 01:17:04,881
"Pandora's Hope" is now a film.

1495
01:17:04,924 --> 01:17:07,057
So it has a life.

1496
01:17:07,100 --> 01:17:10,321
It's not a newspaper article

1497
01:17:10,364 --> 01:17:12,279
that, you know,
is yesterday's news,

1498
01:17:12,323 --> 01:17:13,585
buried and gone.

1499
