in New York City.

1503
01:17:26,859 --> 01:17:28,165
- You're kidding.

1504
01:17:28,208 --> 01:17:30,471
- Isn't that amazing?

1505
01:17:30,515 --> 01:17:32,343
- That's fabulous.

1506
01:17:32,386 --> 01:17:37,435
In my heart,
I've always been the person

1507
01:17:37,478 --> 01:17:40,612
who is disturbed by things,

1508
01:17:40,656 --> 01:17:42,875
wants to see a change,

1509
01:17:42,919 --> 01:17:45,922
and looks for a way
in which to reach people

1510
01:17:45,965 --> 01:17:47,532
to ring the bell

1511
